<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="139">
<emphasis bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="139">Measurements</emphasis>
(holotype). Body length: 3.11; head length: 0.62; head width: 1.51; lengths of antennomeres I-IV: 0.14-0.33-0.25-0.60; lengths of labiomeres I-IV: 0.47-0.27-0.38-0.46; pronotum length: 0.83; pronotum width: 1.39; scutellum length: 0.72; scutellum width: 0.79.
</paragraph>
